# Project Structure

- `app/` - Next.js App Router directory
  - `(logged-out)/` - Route group for non-authenticated users
  - `(main)/` - Main application routes
  - `admin/` - Admin panel routes
  - `api/` - API routes (server actions preferred over these)
- `components/` - Reusable React components
  - `sections/` - Larger page sections (like [daily-comment-section.tsx](mdc:components/sections/daily-comment-section.tsx))
  - `shared/` - Components shared across multiple features
  - `tables/` - Table components
  - `ui/` - Basic UI components (mostly shadcn-based)
- `lib/` - Utility functions and library code
  - `generated/` - Generated code (e.g., Prisma client)
- `prisma/` - Database schema and migrations
- `public/` - Static assets
  - `images/` - Image assets

  - `uploads/` - User-uploaded content